data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Attention Investors! CASH ONLY! No wraps or assign deals. 5 Beds 3 baths with a built-in pool on a cul-de-sac and a large lot… The good, newer AC and roof. Roof is apx 8 years old. AC & ductwork is apx. 5 years old. The home needs a complete refresh. Lot’s of upside. Run your numbers. Garage has been converted to a large in-law suite with separate entrance and private bathroom and small bonus room.
